rows.label: tlk45200153_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Alba Margen is a pretty
big city, right?

rows.label: tlk45200153_01_msg0002
rows.name:
The buildings are pretty huge, and there
are all kinds of different shops. Apparently
folk who visit get lost a lot.

rows.label: tlk45200153_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Shops are on the central main street.
This way's all houses and warehouses,
and down the opposite way's the inn.

rows.label: tlk45200153_01_msg0004
rows.name:
But if you really get lost,
it helps to get up on the
roofs. Good view from up there!
